title: Aladdin's Eatery
typeOfFood: Lacto, Mediterranean, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Franchise chain Mediterranean/Middle Eastern food restaurant. Large menu with veg suitable items including hummus, baba, tabouli, falafel, vegetable soup, chili, lentil soup, salads, wraps, mujadara plate, and pita pizzas. An assortment of teas, juices, and smoothies. Sometimes serves locally made vegan cookies.
